<?php $__env->startSection('postContent'); ?><p>To provide a Mathematics programme that will develop in students, the skills, concepts, understandings, and attitudes, which will enable them to cope confidently with the mathematics of everyday life. This course provides a continuing Mathematics programme appropriate for students who undertook a Level 1 Mathematics course. The following topics are studies: Number, Measurement, Space and Shape, Geometry, Graphs, Algebra, Statistics and Probability. This course is completely internally assessed.</p><?php $__env->stopSection(); ?>
